<p>I am getting a response in the form of json string.In response one field could be array of object or a simple object for eg.</p>  <p>Type 1.</p>  <pre><code>[{"0":1, "1":"name1", "id":1, "name":"name1"} , {"0":2, "1":"name2", "id":2, "name":"name2"}] </code></pre>  <p>Type 2.</p>  <pre><code>{"0":1, "1":"name1", "id":1, "name":"name1"} </code></pre>  <p>To handle this case I have created two model classes one for array of object and one for single object.</p>  <p>Is there any smart way to handle this.</p>